# Mastermind Monorepo

## Architecture

```
mastermind/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ apps/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ web/            ‚Üí Next.js 15 + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4       :3000
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ admin/          ‚Üí Next.js 15 + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4       :3002
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/           ‚Üí Mintlify documentation                         :3003
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ react-native/   ‚Üí Expo + Expo Router + NativeWind
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ remotion/       ‚Üí Remotion video generation                      :3004
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ os/             ‚Üí Desktop environment (Next.js 15 + shadcn/ui)   :7777
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ server/         ‚Üí Fastify + Swagger API server                   :3001
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packages/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ app-config/     ‚Üí Centralized app metadata, branding, and assets
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ blueprint-cli/  ‚Üí npx blueprint CLI (scaffold & workspace commands)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ db/             ‚Üí Drizzle ORM + Neon PostgreSQL (shared schema)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ eslint-config/  ‚Üí Shared ESLint configs
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ typescript-config/ ‚Üí Shared TypeScript configs
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ prompts/            ‚Üí AI prompt library (branding, design systems, components)
```

## Package Relationships

- `apps/web`, `apps/admin`, `apps/os`, and `apps/server` depend on `@repo/db`
- All apps use `@repo/app-config`, `@repo/eslint-config`, and `@repo/typescript-config`
- Each Next.js app has its own independent shadcn/ui install

## Key Commands

- `pnpm dev` ‚Äî start all apps
- `pnpm dev:web` / `pnpm dev:admin` / `pnpm dev:server` / `pnpm dev:os` ‚Äî start individual apps
- `pnpm db:push` ‚Äî push schema to database
- `pnpm db:generate` ‚Äî generate migrations
- `pnpm db:studio` ‚Äî open Drizzle Studio
- `pnpm sync-config` ‚Äî sync app-config branding, theme, and assets to all apps

## Package Manager

This project uses **pnpm 10** with workspaces. Always use `pnpm` (never npm or yarn).

## Runtime

Node.js >= 23 (`.nvmrc` is provided ‚Äî run `nvm use`).
